pageContext.claim: “‘Because the House has already voted against the Impeachment Proceeding, the current inquiry is totally invalid. The current sham of a so-called investigation is nothing more than an unconstitutional power grab. It needs to end.’  @JasonChaffetz  @seanhannity  Corrupt Adam Schiff”
pageContext.analysis: That's not how it works. The House voted down several attempts to impeach Trump before it began the impeachment inquiry involving Ukraine. That's not invalid, a sham, unconstitutional or a power grab.
